# Data Directory

Place your CSV data files in this directory.

## Expected Format

The system expects CSV files with:
- Header row with column names
- Numeric or categorical features
- Optional target column for supervised learning

## Example Structure

```
data/
├── .gitkeep
├── sample_data.csv
├── training_data.csv
└── test_data.csv
```

## Notes

- Large data files (>100MB) should be added to `.gitignore`
- Consider using CSV compression (gzip) for large datasets
- Ensure proper encoding (UTF-8 recommended)
